<br>
2. Her first order was sending The Giant Squid to terrorize the harbors of the Path of Red which he had no problem doing. The Path of Red however was confused as the human recited passages from some book called .. well Orchid something. <br>
<br>
3. During the state of confusion she had Recycled An Animal who was some Fight Club fanatic possibly environmentalist who was pro killing animals so long as you recycled them.. or something lead a small group of environmentalist to kidnap the confused path of red and end this run on sentence. The Run on sentence being ended caused great rejoicing. &quot;Yeah&quot;. <br>
<br>
4. Recycled an animal twitched a few times, suffered 3 seizures and upon recovering did as Joan Of Arp directed and lead a group of Sheep who he thought where crazy people but in fact where the real sheep to attack the path of red. <br>
<br>
5. He was successful in kidnapping them but only after they had laughed at him, ate the three sheep drank a keg of beer and fell asleep drunk. He then returned them and the man who thought he was a squid back to Joan of Arp. This caused much rejoicing and drooling amongst the people. &quot;Yeah&quot;. <br>
