<br>
We do know however that large pyramids where once build dedicated to their worship and practice, the members ranged in the hundreds. When sane missionaries came the viewed it as an abomination and began persecuting the Path of Yellow. <br>
<br>
The persecution went on four years until most members had been killed in temple filled blooth baths. The sane ones where known to the followers as The Path of Red from those days forth. Most followers where dispersed all that remained of one psychotic following was the the original triangle. The Telepathic Banana, The Mad Man of Yellow, and The Great Sheep King of Yellow. <br>
<br>
